headline: Boeing (BA) Valuation Check After Earnings Beat And Major 737 MAX Orders From Air Cambodia And Air India
summary: Boeing (BA) is back in focus after reporting full year 2025 results that beat market expectations, returning to profitability alongside fresh commercial momentum from new 737 MAX orders with Air Cambodia and Air India. See our latest analysis for Boeing.
